  "full_text": "An update for net-snmp is now available for Red Hat Enterprise Linux 10.\n\nThe net-snmp packages provide various libraries and tools for the Simple Network Management Protocol (SNMP), including an SNMP library, an extensible agent, tools for requesting or setting information from SNMP agents, tools for generating and handling SNMP traps, a version of the netstat command which uses SNMP, and a Tk/Perl Management Information Base (MIB) browser.Bug Fix(es) and Enhancement(s): Update net-snmp to support post-quantum cryptography in TLS [rhel-10.1.z] (JIRA:RHEL-112338)"
